PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of NANCY HUSTON, of Whitehorse, Yukon Territory, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Tourism Commission to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Pat Corbett, whose term has expired.
